gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Knicks 113, Wizards 109
gameRecap.excerpt: The Knicks defeated the Wizards, 113-109. Jalen Brunson led the way with 41 points (20 in the 4th quarter) along with eight rebounds and eight assists for the Knicks, Julius Randle added 21 points, eight rebounds, and five assists in the victory. Jordan Poole tallied 24 points and four rebounds for the Wizards in the defeat. The Knicks improve to 25-17, while the Wizards fall to 7-33.
